@/**
 * AUTHOR: jewright
 * DATE/TIME:  Mar 28, 2005
 * PROGRAM/FILENAME: net.cybertristam.service.FileStatisticsServiceImpl
 * EXPLANATION:
 * TEST DATA & EXPECTED RESULTS:
 * ENTRY:
 * EXPECTED RESULTS:
 * REVISION HISTORY:
 * VERSION NUMBER     DATE       AUTHOR
 *     1           Mar 28, 2005      jewright
